::EndBringer/Demise/Greven::

EndBringer looks down at Astrotrain as he approaches. All three of 
the visiting bots were at least 3 feet taller than this one.

"I'm a warrior in Killfest's faction," he replies, deciding that 
Astrotrain wouldn't be a challenge in a fight, "We're interested in 
an alliance as well. If I got contact of my commander, he could 
exchange information with you."



--- In nbwrpg@egroups.com, "rAuq" <rauq@t...> wrote:
> Astrotrain nods and says to Motormaster, "Just as it should be."
> Then he turns to the new bots and goes over to meet them.
> "And who are you bots? We are interested in some sort of alliance. 
> Being new here we would like to exchange information."
